35#ifndef _BUFFER_H_
36#define _BUFFER_H_
37
38typedef struct saslc__buffer_context_t saslc__buffer_context_t;
39typedef struct saslc__buffer32_context_t saslc__buffer32_context_t;
40
41saslc__buffer_context_t *saslc__buffer_create(saslc_sess_t *, size_t);
42void saslc__buffer_destroy(saslc__buffer_context_t *);
43ssize_t saslc__buffer_fetch(saslc__buffer_context_t *, const uint8_t *,
44 size_t, uint8_t **, size_t *);
45
46saslc__buffer32_context_t *saslc__buffer32_create(saslc_sess_t *, size_t);
47void saslc__buffer32_destroy(saslc__buffer32_context_t *);
48ssize_t saslc__buffer32_fetch(saslc__buffer32_context_t *, const uint8_t *,
49 size_t, uint8_t **, size_t *);
50
51#endif /* ! _BUFFER_H_ */
